Game Operation Executive
Responsibilities
Garena Indonesia is now expanding the team and looking for young, energetic and talented people to join as GAME OPERATION EXECUTIVE, which will hold the responsibilities to :  Communicate directly with playersBuild strong relationships and maintain a visible external presencemaintain the community strategy including methods for engagement, moderation policies, content building, and outreach initiativesMonitor discussion forums and other communication media to identify common player issuesExecute planned online and offline eventsKeeping track of daily key performance indicators and ensure that the products are generating revenue The requirements for this position are :  Female is PreferredMinimum Diploma Degree from any majorGood communication and written skillsCustomer focused and enjoys interacting with peopleGood event management and interpersonal skillsA strong team player with positive learning and working attitudePreferred active and experienced in social mediaLove games is an advantage Just send your latest updated CV with copy of ID and latest education certificate to HR-ID@GARENA.COM (in .doc or .pdf format, with size maximum 500kb).
